{
  "stem": "1061.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So one way or another, he was gotten rid of, whether by shooting by the Ukrainian, or by shooting by the Gestapo, or by-- by-- by being taken out with 20 other men into the woods and being shot there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It just didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or on the way to work or whichever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, you see, this was-- however, the one great advantage of being in that camp was that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the people, the majority of the people in that camp, were from my home town, you see?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were still, much as we were-- have already progressed to-- to slave labor and to fear and to horror and malnutrition-- of course, malnutrition-- and we have progressed, you know, on the scale of this design, we have now progressed.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Still, being among people who you know, who know you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were-- as a matter of fact, there were a number of very small children smuggled.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was a young kid, but there were younger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were kids five, six years--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by then I was about 13.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were five and six-year-old kids that they even survived Auschwitz, believe it or not, the kids from my home town.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't survive later, past that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Past the liberation, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they did survive that camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I said, the-- the evacuation of-- of-- the liquidation of the town was in October, 1942.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the camp lasted until the end of June, 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you see, what happened is that there was a kind of a rebellion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't really a rebellion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you know, our-- the camp was surrounded with guards and-- in the towers, on the towers.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
